<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading2"><h2 id=3D"Complex_structure">Complex =
structure</h2><span class=3D"mw-editsection"><span class=3D"mw-editsection-=
bracket">[</span><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=3DAn=
nulus_(mathematics)&amp;action=3Dedit&amp;section=3D2" title=3D"Edit sectio=
n: Complex structure"><span>edit</span></a><span class=3D"mw-editsection-br=
acket">]</span></span></div>
<p>In <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Complex_analysis" title=3D"C=
omplex analysis">complex analysis</a> an <b>annulus</b> <span class=3D"texh=
tml">ann(<i>a</i>; <i>r</i>, <i>R</i>)</span> in the <a href=3D"https://en.=
wikipedia.org/wiki/Complex_plane" title=3D"Complex plane">complex plane</a>=
 is an <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Open_region" class=3D"mw-re=
direct" title=3D"Open region">open region</a> defined as
</p>
<dl><dd><span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span clas=
s=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;">=
<math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\displaystyl=
e r&lt;|z-a|&lt;R.}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle=3D"true" scriptlevel=3D"0">
        <mi>r</mi>
        <mo>&lt;</mo>
        <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
          <mo stretchy=3D"false">|</mo>
        </mrow>
        <mi>z</mi>
        <mo>=E2=88=92<!-- =E2=88=92 --></mo>
        <mi>a</mi>
        <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
          <mo stretchy=3D"false">|</mo>
        </mrow>
        <mo>&lt;</mo>
        <mi>R</mi>
        <mo>.</mo>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">{\displaystyle r&lt;|z-a|&lt=
;R.}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/7067cf6785dc372d620df0d22be69e57d1cc21c0" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
